"tid":1084181,"uid":217942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ddb399422ec758be05076036e67235b4c29774","tid":1084181,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:41:29.000Z","msg":"25"},{"pid":"a333671d5f1e4decf43ff5044e711bc449e8a6b8","tid":1084181,"uid":1886,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"兩個月前我開始跳鋼管舞，我覺得自己學得不錯也跳得很開心，然後有些人反應很大，說什麼老師不能跳鋼管舞。<br />\n<br />\n老師不能xxx，老師不能yyy，是我教書以來聽過最多的批評，完全不是圍繞我的教學質素，而是議論我在課室以外穿什麼衣服，有什麼興趣等等。<br />\n<br />\n首先我不知道鋼管舞和做老師有什麼關係，一個老師下了課，她就是一個普通人，她跳鋼管舞的時候是個學生，教鋼管舞的才是老師。<br />\n<br />\n其次，跳鋼管舞會影響我教中文嗎？是會摔倒失憶令我的古文背不出來？如果今天我不是一個老師，是一個會計師，是不是也不能跳鋼管舞？為何唯獨對老師有這樣的要求？<br />\n<br />\n如果再有人跟我說老師不能xxx，我會說，老師不是修女，不用把一生奉獻給上帝，老師有她的生活，下課後要穿什麼做什麼是她的事。<br />\n<br />\n還有，我不是在學校全職當老師（雖然我也覺得學校老師課後有衣著自由但我管不著），我開了補習社，也請了其他老師來教，所以更準確的身份是補習社的投資者。現在我每個星期只教一班DSE，閒時拍拍YouTube片教中文，沒打算做受世俗束縛的那種老師，如果家長擔心子女受我毒害恐怕也沒有機會，因為我不教幼兒，DSE班的名額也很滿了。<br />\n<br />\n我的補習社不會管老師課外的衣著，也不會因為政治取態判老師社會服務令，只關心教學質素，會把老師當作普通人看待。<br />\n<br />\n呢篇講得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MissPunGoodTeacher/photos/a.2033177290257606/2230771147164885/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMissPunGoodTeacher%2Fphotos%2Fa.2033177290257606%2F2230771147164885%2F&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6gu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=9b171a63\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MissPunGoodTeacher/photos/a.2033177290257606/2230771147164885/</a>"},{"pid":"6c231b1c16f45e97b0029cf9fbc2966b5dcc5d35","tid":1084181,"uid":71092,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"又暴動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c896300a69e146197af9baad0c09ecef83600f","tid":1084181,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/30/OqxwsC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F30%2FOqxwsC.png&h=e3c8c916&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"819fe641b37c18d49a5bb260454f3f850d295968","tid":1084181,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/30/d9HLQc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F30%2Fd9HLQc.png&h=6c1806ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8f7c5e970c04edef9db75db42b8e5a8b7f755f9","tid":1084181,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://instagram.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/vp/79be25054a98d9f08fc5cee2d459dd63/5D303430/t51.2885-15/e35/49332805_824927461185578_3530324908522887309_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fvp%2F79be25054a98d9f08fc5cee2d459dd63%2F5D303430%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F49332805_824927461185578_3530324908522887309_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dinstagram.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net&h=c6299ee7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6461a1560355337f5b3a3ffeff3afcde30b74fdc","tid":1084181,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://instagram.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/vp/e1c515f7e971bf430cbaaf8ce91bb2c4/5D2DC893/t51.2885-15/e35/47584497_218820905667198_6743085337960247784_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fvp%2Fe1c515f7e971bf430cbaaf8ce91bb2c4%2F5D2DC893%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F47584497_218820905667198_6743085337960247784_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dinstagram.fhkg4-2